---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Maine Cannabis Market Analysis | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Analysis of Maine's cannabis market size, growth trends, opportunities, and competitive landscape for dispensary owners."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533491414534-19253f53874c?q=80&w=1200&h=400&auto=format&fit=crop"
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Maine Cannabis Market Analysis</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Understanding the opportunity in Maine's cannabis industry</p>
    </div>

    <Callout title="A Land of Opportunity" type="passion">
      Maine's cannabis market is a frontier of possibility. From the coastal towns to the inland cities, there's a unique spirit of independence and quality that defines our local industry. By understanding these market dynamics, you're not just reading data—you're mapping out your path to success in one of the most exciting sectors in the state!
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Overview</h2>
      <p>Maine's cannabis market has grown significantly since retail sales launched in 2020. The combination of medical and adult-use programs creates a substantial opportunity for dispensary operators.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Size & Growth</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Metric</th><th>Estimate</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Total Market Size (2025)</td><td>$200-250M</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Projected Growth (Annual)</td><td>10-15%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Medical Patients</td><td>50,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Adult-Use Customers</td><td>Growing rapidly</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Drivers</h2>
...
        <li>First-mover advantage in new markets</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Further Reading</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources/data" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Market Data & Reports</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal or financial advice. Cannabis regulations are subject to change; always consult with the Maine Office of Cannabis Policy and qualified legal counsel.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
</style>
